content: Very disappointed liked game until the end but wouldn't let me finish it

Super fun and storywise wild! I love the way the story continues developing and the opportunity to spend more time with Raven and the pack! Great characters and memorable moments, do yourself a favor and start playing from episode 1

very good game !
